data.description: Charming brick ranch in St. Clair Shores features a bright interior with a large eat-in kitchen, partially finished basement, and private backyard. Spacious entry living room with hardwood floors and a large front window. Wonderful kitchen with tile floors, tile backsplash and ample cabinet space. Dining room off the kitchen with a sliding glass door to the backyard. Three nice sized bedrooms share a full bath down the hallway. Large partially finished basement provides a great bonus entertainment space, laundry, and storage. Lovely backyard with a privacy fence, patio, and detached two car garage. Great location, walking distance to Lake St. Clair, close to local parks, shopping, and easy freeway access. Welcome Home!
